div class="order-3 flex grow flex-wrap md:hidden md:grow-0"><div class="mt-4 w-full"> <button class="flex justify-center items-center w-full bg-brand-green text-white text-base font-sans font-medium rounded-md hover:cursor-pointer md:text-sm h-11">现在去购物</button></div><div class="mx-2 mt-4 w-full"><div class=" font-sans leading-3 text-black"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-1"> <span class="text-sm font-bold">92.99 美元</span></div><div class="flex items-center gap-x-1 font-bold"><span class="text-xs line-through">$105.99</span><span class="text-sm text-brand-green">节省 $13.00</span></div></div></div></div></div></div><p>这面镜子的内部和外部都有灯，再加上存放耳环、手镯、化妆刷、项链、瓶装产品和其他自我护理必需品的存储空间，它隐藏了我努力保持整洁的所有小东西，而又不会使其难以接近。这是我买过的最有用的装饰品之一。</p><p>另一种选择是升级您的边桌。你需要一个有多个抽屉和隔间的床头柜，这样你就不太可能让它的顶部变成一堆乱七八糟的东西。尝试这样的事情： </p><div class="mb-4 rounded-md py-7 shadow-xl md:py-6"><div class="order-1 mx-auto flex flex-col justify-center md:order-2 md:ml-4 md:w-full md:grow"><div class="block text-center font-akshar text-2xl font-medium leading-7 text-brand-green md:text-left md:text-xl md:leading-6">带无线充电站的床头柜</div><div class="mt-4 hidden md:flex md:justify-between"><div class="self-end"><div class="mb-0 h-11 md:flex md:flex-col md:justify-center"><div class=" font-sans leading-3 text-black"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-1"> <span class="text-sm font-bold">99.99 美元</span></div><div class="flex items-center gap-x-1 font-bold"><span class="text-xs line-through">$139.99</span><span class="text-sm text-brand-green">节省 $40.00</span></div></div></div></div><div class="w-44 self-end"> <button class="flex justify-center items-center w-full bg-brand-green text-white text-base font-sans font-medium rounded-md hover:cursor-pointer md:text-sm h-11">获得优惠</button></div></div></div><div class="order-2 mt-5 h-auto w-full md:order-1 md:mt-0 md:hidden"><div class="flex items-center justify-center" style="aspect-ratio: 16 / 9"><img class="max-h-full max-w-full" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/ar